WEBVTT

00:03:28.670 --> 00:03:31.150
and be the best for our own careers,

00:03:31.174 --> 00:03:33.685
is also what is best for the world.

00:03:34.484 --> 00:03:39.286
So I urge you to shut your eyes,

00:03:39.310 --> 00:03:42.747
and discover the great ideas
that lie inside us;

00:03:43.280 --> 00:03:46.690
to shut your engines
and discover the power of sleep.

00:03:46.714 --> 00:03:47.976
Thank you.

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:50.460
(Applause)